mily:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">4</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:467.8pt"><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 10.06pt; padding-left:4.14pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Make it a requirement on employers to advertise all publicly -funded jobs as av</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ailable for flexible working.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:28.35pt"><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:right"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">4</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">5</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:467.8pt"><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 10.06pt; padding-left:4.14pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Improve the provision of information, advice and guidance to both young people and adults to remove the gender biases which continue to exist and make positive steps to reduce stereotyping in careers advice.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:28.35pt"><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:right"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">46</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:467.8pt"><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 10.06pt; padding-left:4.14pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Look at the recent soundings article from the New Economics Foundation about the benefits of reducing the “normal” full time working week to 30 hours - </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">http://w</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ww.neweconomics.org/blog/entry/its-time-to-change-the-way-we-work-and-care</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:28.35pt"><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:right"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">4</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">7</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-left-color:#eeece1; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:0.5pt; border-right-color:#eeece1; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:0.5pt; border-top-color:#eeece1; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:0.5pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:467.8pt"><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 10.06pt; padding-left:4.14pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">To stimulate greater engagement from the PEI</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">s so they participate in research in relevant disciplines and make recommendations around the retention of women in academia and</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> to facilitate programmes and funding to enable women to update their skills after a caring break.</span></li></ul></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#eeece1; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:0.5pt; border-